.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1249,2130,960,1233]" pageId="0" pageNumber="620">• Dry, moist, wet, pine tropical forests, and human-modified landscapes.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1249,2130,960,1233]" box="[1249,1791,1123,1156]" pageId="0" pageNumber="620">• 2 genera, 2 species, 4 extant taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1249,2130,960,1233]" pageId="0" pageNumber="620">• 1 species Endangered; 1 species Extinct shortly before 1600.</paragraph>
